document_data.mainbody: '''Daranna Brokenspear''' was a high-ranking [[Harper]] ranger agent in the [[High Forest]].{{Cite dragon/430/The Harpers of Waterdeep}}
document_data.History: In [[1486 DR]], Daranna and some of her agents joined [[Khochen]] and [[Vescaras Ammakyl|Vescaras]] to help, and surveil, [[Mehen]] in researching the missing [[Farideh]].
